The Herald Blessings Chidakwa Municipal Reporter
THE MDC-T led by Dr Thokozani Khupe has recalled Harare deputy mayor and Ward 35 Councillor Enoch Mupamawonde and 10 others. <img class="wp-image-506023 size-large" src="https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Councillor-Kufahakutizwi-474x680.jpg" alt="" width="474" height="680" srcset="https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Councillor-Kufahakutizwi-474x680.jpg 474w, https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Councillor-Kufahakutizwi-251x360.jpg 251w, https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Councillor-Kufahakutizwi-768x1102.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px" /> Cllr Munyaradzi Kufahakutizwi The other recalled councillors are Lovemore Makuwerere (Ward 24), Gilbert Hadebe (Ward 39), Munyaradzi Kufahakutizwi (Ward 19), Simon Mapanzure (Ward 34), Charles Chidhagu (Ward 30), Keith Charumbira (Ward 8). <img class="wp-image-506025 size-large" src="https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Lovemore-Makuwerere-475x680.jpg" alt="" width="475" height="680" srcset="https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Lovemore-Makuwerere.jpg 475w, https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Lovemore-Makuwerere-251x360.jpg 251w" sizes="(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px" /> Cllr Lovemore Makuwerere Also recalled are Councillors Steven Dhliwayo (Ward 40), Barnabas Ndira (Ward 21), Chihoma Runyowa (Ward 29) and Charles Nyatsuro (Ward 6). <img class="wp-image-506028 size-large" src="https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Simon-Mapanzure-507x680.jpg" alt="" width="507" height="680" srcset="https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Simon-Mapanzure.jpg 507w, https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Simon-Mapanzure-268x360.jpg 268w" sizes="(max-width: 507px) 100vw, 507px" /> Cllr Simon Mapanzure Harare City Council is now left with 27 councillors as other seven were also recalled last month. <img class="wp-image-506031 size-large" src="https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Charles-Chidagu-491x680.jpg" alt="" width="491" height="680" srcset="https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Charles-Chidagu.jpg 491w, https://www.herald.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/09/Charles-Chidagu-260x360.jpg 260w" sizes="(max-width: 491px) 100vw, 491px" /> Cllr Charles Chidagu The seven are; former mayor Hebert Gomba, Lovemore Makuwerere, Hammy Madzingira, Costa Mande, Kudzai Kadzombe, Happymore Gotora and Gilbert Hadebe. A quorum is supposed to made up of 17 councillors.